          <title>The Onion Outbids First United American Companies for Infowars at Bankruptcy Auction</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The satirical news outlet The Onion has been named the winning bidder for Infowars in a bankruptcy auction, but the Jones-affiliated company First United American Companies is disputing the result, alleging fraud and collusion.]]></description>
